<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="37" /> at <placeName key="tgn,2119163" n="1.000 3" reg="meadow bridge, fayette, west virginia" authname="tgn,2119163">Meadow Bridges</placeName>, <placeName reg="Hanover county, Virginia" key="tgn,1002451" authname="tgn,1002451">Hanover county</placeName>, the residence of his grandparents, on the <dateStruct value="-09-12" full="yes" authname="--09-12"><day reg="12" full="yes">12th</day> of <month reg="09" full="yes">September</month></dateStruct>, <persName n="Marcus,,Shelton,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00020" reg="default:Marcus,Shelton,,," authname="marcus,shelton"><foreName full="yes">Shelton</foreName> <surname full="yes">Marcus</surname></persName>, in his <num value="5" type="ordinal">fifth</num> year, only son of <persName n="Maria,,Ann,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00021" reg="default:Maria,Ann,,," authname="maria,ann"><foreName full="yes">Ann</foreName> <surname full="yes">Maria</surname></persName> and <persName n="Miles,,Marcus,E.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00022" reg="default:Miles,Marcus,E.,," authname="miles,marcus,e."><foreName full="yes">Marcus</foreName> <foreName full="yes">E.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Miles</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Buckingham, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,2002149" authname="tgn,2002149">Buckingham county, Virginia</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="38" /> a bud just lent us for a while to waft its fragrance around; but, oh!

<milestone unit="sentence" n="39" />the chilly winds of <dateStruct value="-09-" full="yes" authname="--09"><month reg="09" full="yes">September</month></dateStruct> have swept it from this earth forever to bloom perpetually in a heavenly clime! </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="40" /> <cit><q direct="unspecified"> <lg type="stanza" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
