<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="42" /> On the <dateStruct value="--12" full="yes" authname="---12"><day reg="12" full="yes">12th instant</day></dateStruct>, of consumption, <persName n="Frischcorn,,Bernard,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00023" reg="default:Frischcorn,Bernard,,," authname="frischcorn,bernard"><foreName full="yes">Bernard</foreName> <surname full="yes">Frischcorn</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="55years" type="date">fifty-five years</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="43" /> His funeral will take place from <placeName key="tgn,7013172" n="1.000 13" reg="saint john,new brunswick,canada,north and central america" authname="tgn,7013172">St. John</placeName>'s (<orgName n="Lutheran Church" type="church">Lutheran) Church</orgName> at <time value="3oclock">3 o'clock</time> to-day.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="44" />Friends and acquaintances are invited to attend. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="45" /> "Blessed are the dead, who die in the <rs>Lord</rs>." </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="46" /> <placeName reg="Baltimore, Baltimore Independent City, Maryland" key="tgn,7013352" authname="tgn,7013352">Baltimore</placeName> and <placeName reg="Washington, District of Columbia, United States" key="tgn,7013962" authname="tgn,7013962">Washington</placeName> papers please copy. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="47" /> * </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p> On the morning of the <dateStruct value="-09-13" full="yes" authname="--09-13"><day reg="13" full="yes">13th</day> of <month reg="09" full="yes">September</month></dateStruct>, of <sic>diptheria</sic> and whooping-cough, <persName n="Crenshaw,,Mary,F.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00024" reg="default:Crenshaw,Mary,F.,," authname="crenshaw,mary,f."><foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName> <foreName full="yes">F.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Crenshaw</surname></persName>, daughter of <persName><foreName full="yes">John</foreName></persName> B. and <persName n="Crenshaw,,Judith,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00025" reg="default:Crenshaw,Judith,A.,," authname="crenshaw,judith,a."><foreName full="yes">Judith</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Crenshaw</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="10months" type="date">ten months</measure> and <measure n="4days" type="date">four days</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="48" /> Her funeral will take place from her father's residence to-day at <time value="10am">10 o'clock A. M.</time> The friends and relatives of the family are invited to attend without further notice. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="49" /> <placeName reg="Philadelphia, Philadelphia, Pennsylvania" key="tgn,7014406" authname="tgn,7014406">Philadelphia</placeName> papers please copy. * </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="50" /> On <dateStruct value="-09-13" full="yes" authname="--09-13"><day type="name" full="yes">Tuesday</day>, <month reg="09" full="yes">September</month> <day reg="13" full="yes">13th</day></dateStruct>, at <time value="12:10oclock">ten minutes past 12 o'clock</time>, of typhoid dysentery, <persName n="Boucher,,Rosey,Lee,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00026" reg="default:Boucher,Rosey,Lee,," authname="boucher,rosey,lee"><foreName full="yes">Rosey</foreName> <foreName full="yes">Lee</foreName> <surname full="yes">Boucher</surname></persName>, daughter of <persName><foreName full="yes">John</foreName></persName> and <persName n="Boucher,,M.,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00027" reg="default:Boucher,M.,A.,," authname="boucher,m.,a."><foreName full="yes">M.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Boucher</surname></persName>, aged <num value="1">one</num> year, <measure n="4months" type="date">four months</measure> and <measure n="21days" type="date">twenty-one days</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="51" /> Her funeral will take place from her parents' residence, on <address><street n="6 Street">Sixth street</street></address>, between <address><street n="Main street">Main</street></address> and <address><street n="Franklin street">Franklin</street></address> streets, this (<dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Wednesday</day></dateStruct>) <time>morning</time>, <dateStruct value="--14" full="yes" authname="---14"><day reg="14" full="yes">14th instant</day></dateStruct>, at <time value="10oclock">10 o'clock</time>. The friends of the family are respectfully invited to attend. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="52" /> "The <rs>Lord</rs> gave and the <rs>Lord</rs> taketh away; blessed be the name of the <rs>Lord</rs>." </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="5" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="53" /> At his residence, on the <dateStruct value="--10" full="yes" authname="---10"><day reg="10" full="yes">10th instant</day></dateStruct>, after a lingering illness, <persName n="Ford,Mister,Larkin,P.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00028" reg="default:Ford,Larkin,P.,," authname="ford,larkin,p."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Larkin</foreName> <foreName full="yes">P.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Ford</surname></persName>, in the <num value="50" type="ordinal">fiftieth</num> year of his age. </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
